'''色當'''（{{lang-en|Sedan}}，{{IPA-en|sə.dɑ̃}}）為[[美国|美国]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[學托擴縣_(堪薩斯州)|學托擴縣]]轄下的城市，也是學托擴縣的[[县城|县城]]。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有1,124人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=March 27, 2011|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
色當設立於1871年<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA154#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=154}}</ref>。此城市的名字以法國阿登省的市鎮[[色當_(阿登省)|色當]]命名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=5015 | title=Profile for Sedan, Kansas | publisher=[[ePodunk|ePodunk]] | accessdate=6 June 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619140739/http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=5015 | archive-date=2017-06-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。色當於1876年升為城市<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Qi9cXyTWt9EC&pg=PA661#v=onepage&q&f=true | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Volume 2 | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=661}}</ref>。

==地理==
色當坐落於北緯37度7分42秒、西經96度11分10秒（亦可表示為37.128472, -96.186220）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102044750/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2011-01-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，大約位在[[纽约|纽约]]與[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]之間連線的中點處。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|2.10|sqkm|sqmi|2}}，全境皆為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

===氣候===
夏季溼熱、冬季不甚乾冷為此地區的氣候特徵。根據[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，色當的氣候屬於[[副热带湿润气候|副热带湿润气候]]（Cfa）<ref>[http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=503741&cityname=Sedan%2C+Kansas%2C+United+States+of+America&units= Climate Summary for Sedan, Kansas]</ref>。

